{"tid":2263504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭安樂死即將合法化","createTime":"2020-10-30T02:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T03:39:07.000Z","uid":367147,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16156241724d863843a781006858f082db0312b8","tid":2263504,"uid":367147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"紐西蘭安樂死和大麻是否合法化的初步公投結果今天出爐，分別有65.2％的選民支持安樂死合法化及53.1%選民反對大麻合法化。<br />\n<br />\n針對這兩項公投，紐西蘭選舉委員會30日僅公布初步點票結果，正式公投結果要等到11月6日才會公布。<br />\n<br />\n根據初步結果，有65.2％的選民支持「終結生命選擇議案」（ End of Life Choice Bill）成為具法律約束力的新法案。若有兩名醫生批准，將允許活不過6個月的絕症患者有機會選擇安樂死。若公投順利通過，新法將於明年11月生效。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/6809/4975187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4975187&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=024220cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/6809/4975187</a>"},{"pid":"ef9e0fa05d7c88b34862752ef526f5b90c185fd7","tid":2263504,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60be864e981ac4ba71732c66ee4749114f7baad2","tid":2263504,"uid":367147,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef9e0fa05d7c88b34862752ef526f5b90c185fd7","tid":2263504,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"可以多個地方揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec554653fb22507947c35ffd9c8fc3d2da7698d","tid":2263504,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"將一車車藍屍送去外國<br />\n強制安樂死"}]}